thread.title: German minister orders examination of Volkswagen cars - newspaper
thread.title_full: German minister orders examination of Volkswagen cars - newspaper | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: German minister orders examination of Volkswagen cars - newspaper
text: BERLIN, Sept 21 German Transport Minister Alexander Dobrindt has ordered an examination of Volkswagen diesel cars, the German newspaper Bild reported on Monday, after the carmaker admitted that it had rigged emissions tests in the United States. (Reporting By John O'Donnell ; Editing by Kevin Liffey )
